105
00:09:28,551 --> 00:09:30,218
In about 10 minutes.

106
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,577
All right.

107
00:09:32,577 --> 00:09:33,910
All right, fine.

108
00:09:45,563 --> 00:09:48,563
(explosion rumbles)

109
00:10:00,576 --> 00:10:04,483
(helicopter whirring distantly)

110
00:10:04,483 --> 00:10:07,150
(ominous music)

111
