256
00:18:07,202 --> 00:18:08,285
Okay, baby.

257
00:18:09,645 --> 00:18:13,062
(moves to ominous music)

258
00:18:14,430 --> 00:18:17,347
(ghostly whispers)

259
00:18:33,217 --> 00:18:35,113
